-7xl mt-4 mb-6 group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">The Pulse</h2><p class="text-xl text-ink-200 font-serif italic mb-4">We engineer cultural milestones</p><p class="text-ink-300 mb-8">Large-scale festivals, intimate speakeasies, bespoke social experiences.</p><div class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-400">Enter →</div></div></div></a></div></section><section class="px-6 py-24 bg-ink-900/30"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><a class="group block" href="/fr/collection"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden lg:order-2"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=1200&amp;q=80" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"/></div><div class="lg:order-1"><span class="label-mono text-gold-400">02</span><h2 class="editorial-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl mt-4 mb-6 group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">The Collection</h2><p class="text-xl text-ink-200 font-serif italic mb-4">True luxury is timeless</p><p class="text-ink-300 mb-8">Elite modern vehicles and meticulously refurbished vintage classics.</p><div class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-400">Enter →</div></div></div></a></div></section><section class="px-6 py-24 "><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><a class="group block" href="/fr/sanctuary"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden "><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542718610-a1d656d1884c?w=1200&amp;q=80" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"/></div><div class=""><span class="label-mono text-gold-400">03</span><h2 class="editorial-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl mt-4 mb-6 group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">The Sanctuary</h2><p class="text-xl text-ink-200 font-serif italic mb-4">Designing the future of h